description	"Bastila Shan

Class Summary:
A defensive blind-casting support role Jedi that can supply teammates with force energy via AOE force energize ability.

Lightsaber Staff:
- Defense (2)
- Deflect (3)
- Can use Staff and Yellow style

Attributes:
- No extra BP drain on jump
- Flipkick

Force Powers:
- Repulse
- Jump (2)
- Push (3)
- Pull (3)
- Seeing (3)
- Block (3)
- Force Blinding (1)
- Force Energize (1)

Shan was found to have an exceptional gift with a Force power known as battle meditation; which increased her allies' morale while demoralizing her enemies. Shan sided with the Jedi Council when the Jedi Knights Revan and Malak rebelled against the Council and joined the Galactic Republic in its war against the invading Mandalorian Neo-Crusaders."
